body_html:
Have you followed the instructions from examples/android/README.md, including the NDK/SDK installation and WORKSPACE editing?

If so, when you build manually with:
bazel build -c opt tensorflow/examples/android:tensorflow_demo --stacktrace --info

Does it give you any more info?

body:
Have you followed the instructions from [examples/android/README.md](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/examples/android/README.md), including the NDK/SDK installation and WORKSPACE editing?

If so, when you build manually with:
`bazel build -c opt tensorflow/examples/android:tensorflow_demo --stacktrace --info`

Does it give you any more info?
